title: Losing Myself: Tootie's May 2016 Mix
description:
Ain't got no time... This Tootie mix is short; short like the time available to put this together this time, and significantly late to boot. It includes a typical EDM set and a lot of tracks that have been in Tootie's musical collection for a while but never included in a modern Tootie mix.

Most tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.

Details:
Format: FLAC, level 7
Length: 1:18:48.177
Average bitrate: 795 kbps
Embedded CUE Sheet

Playback verified with foobar2000. Track notes embedded via comment fields and can be accessed with foobar2000. Track CTRB content ratings also included.

mixcloud.com/CyberTootie/
